name: Wplace Palette (Free Colours)
author: billystorm
description:
A
 palette of all of the free colours available on Wplace. To be used for 
converting images to pixel art to paint on Wplace. This is useful for 
the people that have yet to unlock all the colours available on the 
site, as they take quite a long time to get. A majority of people will 
end up using this palette.
